OL,3,CMexico agrees to host Iran at World
OL,4,CCup instead of US
OL,6,FIran's national football team will
OL,7,Fsleep in Mexico and travel to the US
OL,8,Fon the days of its three World Cup
OL,9,Fmatches after Washington declined to
OL,10,Fhost the squad for the tournament,
OL,11,FMexican President Claudia Sheinbaum
OL,12,Fsaid on Monday.
OL,14,FSheinbaum said Fifa approached her
OL,15,Fgovernment after US officials said
OL,16,Fthey did not want Iran staying in the
OL,17,Fcountry throughout the competition,
OL,18,Feven though Iran is scheduled to play
OL,19,Fthree Group G matches there.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
