OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779872687
OL,3,CMexico agrees to host Iran at World
OL,4,CCup instead of US
OL,6,FThe team will still play its group-
OL,7,Fstage matches in the US, but its
OL,8,Ftraining base has been moved from
OL,9,FTucson, Arizona, to Tijuana, Mexico.
OL,11,FIran's football federation recently
OL,12,Fannounced the move, which was formally
OL,13,Fconfirmed by Fifa on Monday.
OL,15,F"We have no reason to deny them the
OL,16,Fpossibility of staying in Mexico,"
OL,17,FSheinbaum told her daily press
OL,18,Fconference.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
