PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779872687
OL,3,CMexico agrees to host Iran at World
OL,4,CCup instead of US
OL,6,FThe decision comes amid the ongoing
OL,7,Fwar in Iran, which began after joint
OL,8,FUS-Israeli strikes on February 28.
OL,10,FOn Monday, the US said it had carried
OL,11,Fout "self-defence" strikes on Iran,
OL,12,Fdespite President Donald Trump stating
OL,13,Fthat negotiations between the two
OL,14,Fnations are "proceeding nicely".
OL,16,FTeams use base camps to train before
OL,17,Fand after matches during the
OL,18,Ftournament, which runs from June 11 to
OL,19,FJuly 19 and is being co-hosted by the
OL,20,FUS, Canada and Mexico.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
