PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779872687
OL,3,CMexico agrees to host Iran at World
OL,4,CCup instead of US
OL,6,FThe possibility of moving Iran's base
OL,7,Fhad been discussed for months because
OL,8,Fof uncertainty surrounding the
OL,9,Fconflict in the Middle East and wider
OL,10,Fsecurity concerns.
OL,12,FUS sanctions on Iran were also
OL,13,Fexpected to complicate the team's stay
OL,14,Fin America.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
