PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779872687
OL,3,CMexico agrees to host Iran at World
OL,4,CCup instead of US
OL,6,FThe US State Department said on Monday
OL,7,Fthat Trump had made clear Iran's team
OL,8,Fwould be welcome to take part in the
OL,9,Ftournament, although it did not
OL,10,Fcomment on where the squad would stay.
OL,12,FSheinbaum said her government was
OL,13,Fcontinuing to work with Fifa to
OL,14,Ffinalise arrangements ahead of the
OL,15,Fcompetition.
OL,17,FIran's football team is due to play
OL,18,Fmatches in Inglewood, California,
OL,19,Fagainst New Zealand on June 25 and
OL,20,FBelgium six days later, before facing
OL,21,FEgypt in Seattle on June 26.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
